arts.ttl: Freiburg survive late Holstein Kiel fightback to secure maximum points
arts.sum: Visiting forward Phil Harres gave Freiburg a real scare when netting a late brace but the hosts ultimately did enough thanks to an earlier own goal, Christian Günter's free kick and a neat Vincenzo Grifo finish. Christian Günter celebrates his stunning free-kick goal that doubled Freiburg's lead against Holstein Kiel in the 38th minute.

arts.ttl: Preview: Freiburg vs. Holstein Kiel - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Saturday's Bundesliga clash between Freiburg and Holstein Kiel, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.

arts.ttl: Freiburg vs. Holstein Kiel preview: Can the visitors end their wait for an away win?
arts.sum: Holstein Kiel will attempt to claim their first Bundesliga away victory when they travel to Europa-Park Stadion for Saturday’s clash with Freiburg.

arts.ttl: Out-of-favor Freiburg defender reportedly set for Wolfsburg move
arts.sum: VfL Wolfsburg are understood to be close to signing SC Freiburg defender Kiliann Sildillia.

arts.ttl: Kiel loan Puchacz out to England
arts.sum: Holstein Kiel wingback Tymoteusz Puchacz is headed to the Isle on loan for the duration of the season.
